Text: RE Cc I will forward this to Dutch Dutch try it now on your NT machine call if probs x Original Message From Pechersky Julie Sent Tuesday April PM To Sieckman John Subject FW John Becky reenabled Dutch Quigley so that he is on both the old servers and the Digital What is the next step Original Message From Becky McGraw ENRON mailtoIMCEANOTESBeckyMcGrawCbeckycqgEcomE NRONcom Sent Tuesday April PM To Pechersky Julie Subject RE Julie I reenabled his old system that went off last night Both systems will be functional with the old one going off on April th If you need longer just let me know I have been putting the latest upgrades to allow both systems to run for at least two weeks before cancellation of the old one If you would like that to be a day parallel then I can do that to be on the safe sideactually I will just start doing that so that there is plenty of time for the transition Becky Original Message From Pechersky Julie mailto Sent Tuesday April AM To Subject becky I think that Dutch Quigley has been moved to the Digital feed but is there a way to allow him to run simultaneously on both temporarily Julie
